Where I have put "Type Your Name Here", put your name there, change the part where it says public class "JavaCalculator", to the name you chose your file to be called.

Run it, and it will say
Enter the first number:

1.Put in any number you wish, it might be 1 digit long, or 10 digits long, its your choice, then after you have put your number in press enter.

Then after that it will say
Enter the second number:

Again repeat step 1, if you put 2 in as your first number and 3 as your second, it will say: 5.0
